            "title": "The Diversity of Trematodes in Myotis Bats (Chiroptera, Vespertilionidae) from the Samarskaya Luka (European Russia)",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Nadezhda Yu.",
                    "lastName": "Kirillova"
